text: Jingga 13 is a Malaysian first national Non profit organisation closely related to People's Justice Party (PKR) dedicated in supporting the Reformasi movement in Malaysia and was labeled as pro-Pakatan Rakyat.Jingga 13 holds brief protest Jingga 13 is also a PKR's supported anti-corruption movement NGO.Zakat: Jingga 13 mahu Agong pecat Jamil Khir jika tidak minta maaf Malay == References == == External links == * Official website Jingga 13 * Official Facebook Jingga 13 Category:Political organisations based in Malaysia Category:Non-profit organisations based in Malaysia Category:2011 establishments in Malaysia
